page.title: 17LIFE STYLES
page.content: {Fashion}has already changed alot in the 1980's.In our school we don't have a school uniform.Everyone wears what they like.Some children wear jump suits.Others wear just plain skirts.People are saying that the 60's look is coming back into fashion because of the{tight skirts and v backs.People think more about fashion than they did 900years ago! Some young people have their ears pierced about 10 times in each ear.This summer 1985,the shoe craze is plastic sandles.Hair styles are different they are'nt what they were. Not straight and boring.They have pink,green,and bleached.Bikes are now a craze.BMX's are the thing.A{BMX}has got very big wheels they some times have stunt nuts on, the seats are very hard to sit on.The pop groups I like are{Wham,Frankie.}
